# 03-Scalability-Security

## Mandates

- **Transactions**: All Stripe payment logic and webhook handlers must be robust, idempotent, and secure.
- **Authentication**: All user state must be managed via an external provider (Auth.js/Clerk).
- **Environment**: All configuration must be manageable via environment variables (.env).